@page
@model PCRModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "PCR Activities";
    ViewData["BodyClass"] = "pcr-page";
}

<!-- ── PCR HERO (header + reflection merged) ── -->
<div class="pcr-hero">
    <div class="pcr-hero-inner">
        <p class="section-label">Professional &amp; Career Readiness</p>
        <h1 class="pcr-hero-title">PCR Activities</h1>
        <div class="pcr-hero-divider"></div>
        <p class="pcr-hero-sub">My College Journey</p>
        <p class="pcr-hero-body">
            Looking back on my time at Western Washington University, I can clearly see how my experiences helped
            shape my professional development. When I first began pursuing my education, I was working as a
            custodian during the uncertainty of the COVID period and trying to determine the direction I wanted my
            career to take. That experience motivated me to invest more seriously in my education and pursue
            opportunities that would help me grow professionally. Through my coursework at WWU, I developed
            stronger analytical and problem-solving skills while learning how businesses use technology and
            organizational strategies to operate effectively. Attending professional events and networking
            opportunities helped me become more comfortable communicating with professionals and discussing my
            ideas in professional environments. My work experience at LAZ Parking allowed me to apply what I was
            learning in school to real workplace situations, which strengthened my organization, communication,
            and time-management skills. The internship project where I developed a web application showed me how
            technical skills can directly improve business operations. These experiences helped me realize that
            combining technical knowledge with strong communication and collaboration skills creates real value
            in organizations. Moving forward, I plan to apply everything I have learned by pursuing a career
            where I can design systems and solutions that help businesses operate more efficiently while
            continuing to grow professionally.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="points-summary">
    <div class="points-card">
        <div class="points-card-dot dot-ethics"></div>
        <div class="points-card-label">Ethics &amp; Professionalism</div>
        <div class="points-card-value">5 <span>pts</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="points-card">
        <div class="points-card-dot dot-edia"></div>
        <div class="points-card-label">Equity, Diversity &amp; Inclusion</div>
        <div class="points-card-value">5 <span>pts</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="points-card">
        <div class="points-card-dot dot-comm"></div>
        <div class="points-card-label">Professional Communication</div>
        <div class="points-card-value">5 <span>pts</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="points-card">
        <div class="points-card-dot dot-career"></div>
        <div class="points-card-label">Career Preparation</div>
        <div class="points-card-value">10 <span>pts</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="points-card total">
        <div class="points-card-label">Total Points</div>
        <div class="points-card-value">25 <span>/ 25</span></div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr class="section-divider" />

<!-- ── ETHICS & PROFESSIONALISM ── -->
<div class="pcr-category">
    <div class="category-header">
        <div class="category-header-left">
            <div class="category-dot dot-ethics"></div>
            <h2 class="category-title">Ethics &amp; Professionalism</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="category-points ethics-pts">5 points</span>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-grid">

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap ethics-bar">
                <img src="~/files/system_design.png" alt="MIS 321" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">MIS 321 – Systems Analysis and Design</span>
                    <span class="card-badge ethics-badge">3 pts</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">Fall Quarter 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    In Fall Quarter 2025 I took MIS 321: Systems Analysis and Design at Western Washington University.
                    The course focused on how organizations analyze operational problems and design information systems
                    that improve efficiency and decision making. During the quarter I participated in assignments where
                    we mapped business processes, identified inefficiencies, and proposed system improvements. These
                    activities helped me understand how system analysts gather requirements from stakeholders and
                    translate those needs into technical solutions. One thing I particularly liked about the course was
                    seeing how technology can directly solve real organizational problems rather than existing only as
                    abstract tools. The projects also helped me realize how important clear communication is when
                    working between technical teams and business managers. I developed stronger analytical thinking and
                    problem-solving skills while evaluating how systems impact business operations. In my future career
                    I plan to apply these skills when analyzing business processes and designing technology solutions
                    that improve efficiency while maintaining strong ethical and professional standards.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap ethics-bar">
                <img src="~/files/dcholarship.jpg" alt="Scholarship Application" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Scholarship Application – Latino Community Fund of Washington</span>
                    <span class="card-badge ethics-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">July 3, 2023</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On July 3, 2023 I submitted a scholarship application to the Latino Community Fund of Washington.
                    The application required writing several essays explaining my background, my educational goals, and
                    the career path I hope to pursue after graduation. While preparing the application I spent time
                    reflecting on how my personal experiences influenced my decision to pursue higher education. I
                    carefully reviewed and revised my essays to make sure my ideas were organized clearly and
                    communicated in a professional way. I liked that the process pushed me to step back and think about
                    the bigger picture of my education and long-term goals. Writing the application strengthened my
                    professional writing and self-reflection skills. It also helped me practice presenting my goals and
                    experiences in a clear and professional format. In my future career I will use these communication
                    skills when applying for opportunities and presenting my work to others.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap ethics-bar">
                <img src="~/files/chess.jpg" alt="WWU Chess Club" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Member of the WWU Chess Club</span>
                    <span class="card-badge ethics-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">Winter Quarter 2023 – Present</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    Since Winter Quarter 2023 I have been a member of the Western Washington University Chess Club.
                    The club meets regularly on campus where students play chess, discuss strategies, and challenge
                    each other to competitive games. I joined because I have always enjoyed chess and wanted an
                    activity that would challenge my strategic thinking outside of coursework. During games I
                    frequently analyze multiple moves ahead and evaluate how my opponent might respond before making
                    a decision. This experience helped me develop patience, focus, and the ability to think critically
                    under pressure. I also enjoyed meeting students from different majors who shared a similar interest
                    in strategy and problem solving. Participating in the club strengthened my analytical thinking and
                    decision-making skills. In my future career I will apply the same strategic mindset when
                    approaching complex business or technology challenges.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<!-- ── EQUITY, DIVERSITY, INCLUSION & ACCESSIBILITY ── -->
<div class="pcr-category">
    <div class="category-header">
        <div class="category-header-left">
            <div class="category-dot dot-edia"></div>
            <h2 class="category-title">Equity, Diversity, Inclusion &amp; Accessibility</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="category-points edia-pts">5 points</span>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-grid">

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap edia-bar">
                <img src="~/files/orgbehavior.png" alt="MGMT 311" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">MGMT 311 – Organizational Behavior</span>
                    <span class="card-badge edia-badge">3 pts</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">Winter Quarter 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    In Winter Quarter 2025 I took MGMT 311: Organizational Behavior at Western Washington University.
                    The course explored how individuals behave in organizations and how leadership, communication, and
                    workplace culture influence performance. During the class I participated in discussions and case
                    studies that examined how teams operate in real workplace environments. One topic that stood out
                    to me was how diversity of perspectives can improve decision making and problem solving. I enjoyed
                    analyzing real scenarios where leadership styles and communication strategies influenced the
                    outcome of team dynamics. These discussions helped me understand the importance of creating
                    inclusive and collaborative work environments. The course strengthened my awareness of how
                    workplace culture affects motivation and productivity. In my future career I plan to apply these
                    lessons by encouraging collaboration, respecting diverse perspectives, and contributing to positive
                    team environments.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap edia-bar">
                <img src="~/files/dia-de-los.jpg" alt="Dia de los Muertos" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Día de los Muertos Ofrenda Reception</span>
                    <span class="card-badge edia-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">October 14, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On October 14, 2025 I attended the Día de los Muertos Ofrenda Reception hosted on campus at
                    Western Washington University. The event included traditional ofrenda displays honoring loved ones
                    who had passed away, decorated with candles, marigolds, photographs, and meaningful objects. As I
                    walked through the displays I listened to organizers explain the cultural significance of the
                    tradition and how it celebrates remembrance and heritage. Because I have Mexican heritage,
                    attending the event felt personally meaningful and helped me connect with an important cultural
                    tradition. I also enjoyed seeing students from many different backgrounds attending and learning
                    about the celebration. Events like this help build awareness and appreciation for different
                    cultures within the university community. I gained a deeper understanding of how cultural
                    traditions bring communities together. In my future career I hope to carry that same respect and
                    awareness when working with people from diverse backgrounds.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap edia-bar">
                <img src="~/files/sipnchill.jpg" alt="Sip n Chill" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Sip n Chill – SACNAS &amp; Japanese Student Association</span>
                    <span class="card-badge edia-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">March 6, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On March 6, 2025 I attended the Sip n Chill event hosted by SACNAS and the Japanese Student
                    Association at Western Washington University. The event created a relaxed environment where
                    students from different organizations could meet and talk with each other. During the event I
                    spoke with several students about their majors, academic interests, and experiences at Western.
                    These conversations allowed me to learn about perspectives and experiences that were different
                    from my own. I appreciated how informal the setting was because it encouraged genuine conversations
                    and connections. It helped me understand how diverse communities on campus contribute to a broader
                    exchange of ideas. The experience strengthened my communication and interpersonal skills while
                    interacting with people from different backgrounds. In my future career I hope to bring the same
                    openness and respect for diverse viewpoints into the teams I work with.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<!-- ── PROFESSIONAL COMMUNICATION ── -->
<div class="pcr-category">
    <div class="category-header">
        <div class="category-header-left">
            <div class="category-dot dot-comm"></div>
            <h2 class="category-title">Professional Communication</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="category-points comm-pts">5 points</span>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-grid">

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap comm-bar">
                <img src="~/files/confidence-career-fair.jpg" alt="Career Fair" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Confidence at the Career Fair – Speaker Panel &amp; Networking</span>
                    <span class="card-badge comm-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">October 16, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On October 16, 2025 I attended the "Confidence at the Career Fair" speaker panel hosted by the
                    College of Business and Economics at Western Washington University. During the panel several
                    recruiters discussed how students should introduce themselves and communicate professionally during
                    networking events. I listened to their advice about preparing a clear elevator pitch and asking
                    thoughtful questions when speaking with employers. After the panel I participated in the networking
                    portion and introduced myself to one of the recruiters to ask about skills employers value in
                    candidates. I liked hearing real advice from professionals who regularly evaluate job applicants.
                    The event helped me practice presenting myself confidently and discussing my academic and technical
                    experiences. I gained stronger networking and professional communication skills from the
                    interaction. In my future career I will apply these strategies when communicating with employers,
                    coworkers, and professional contacts.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap comm-bar">
                <img src="~/files/expedia.jpg alt="Expedia Session" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Working at Expedia – Information Session</span>
                    <span class="card-badge comm-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">October 23, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On October 23, 2025 I attended the "Working at Expedia" information session where company
                    representatives discussed career opportunities in the travel technology industry. During the
                    presentation they explained how different teams collaborate to develop technology solutions and
                    improve customer experiences. I listened as they described the importance of communication when
                    engineers, analysts, and business professionals work together on projects. After the presentation
                    I spoke with one of the representatives about what skills help students succeed in
                    technology-focused roles. I liked hearing about the career paths of professionals who work at a
                    large technology company. The discussion helped me understand how communication skills support
                    technical work in real business environments. I gained insight into how professionals translate
                    technical ideas into clear explanations for decision makers. In my future career I will continue
                    developing both technical and communication skills to work effectively on cross-functional teams.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap comm-bar">
                <img src="~/files/sma.jpg" alt="SMA Panel" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">SMA Industry Panel and Reception</span>
                    <span class="card-badge comm-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">October 24, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On October 24, 2025 I attended the SMA Industry Panel and Reception hosted by the Sales and
                    Marketing Association at Western Washington University. During the panel professionals discussed
                    how communication and storytelling are important when presenting ideas to clients and colleagues.
                    I listened to panelists explain how simplifying complex information helps audiences understand
                    business strategies. After the panel I participated in the reception where I introduced myself to
                    a few professionals and asked about their career paths. I enjoyed hearing how they developed their
                    careers and built relationships with clients. The event gave me a chance to practice networking
                    and professional conversation in a real setting. I strengthened my ability to communicate with
                    professionals and ask thoughtful questions. In my future career I will apply these communication
                    skills when presenting ideas and collaborating with colleagues.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap comm-bar">
                <img src="~/files/thriving-ai-era.jpg" alt="AI Era Speaker" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">Thriving in the AI Era: Skills for Today's Job Market</span>
                    <span class="card-badge comm-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">November 18, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On November 18, 2025 I attended a speaker event titled "Thriving in the AI Era: Skills for
                    Today's Job Market." The speaker discussed how artificial intelligence and automation are changing
                    many industries and the types of skills employers now value. I listened as the speaker explained
                    how professionals often need to communicate complex technical systems to managers or stakeholders
                    who may not have technical backgrounds. This topic interested me because I have worked on
                    automation projects and understand the challenge of explaining technical systems clearly. I enjoyed
                    hearing examples of how professionals adapt to technological change. The talk reinforced the
                    importance of communication and collaboration in technology-driven workplaces. I gained a stronger
                    understanding of how technical and interpersonal skills complement each other. In my future career
                    I will continue developing both skill sets so I can communicate technical solutions effectively.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image-wrap comm-bar">
                <img src="~/files/dei-panel.jpg" alt="CBE DEI Panel" onerror="this.closest('.card-image-wrap').classList.add('img-error')" />
                <div class="card-img-placeholder"><span>Add Photo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <span class="card-title">CBE Leadership &amp; DEI Panel Discussion</span>
                    <span class="card-badge comm-badge">1 pt</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">May 29, 2024</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    On May 29, 2024 I attended the CBE Leadership and Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion panel
                    discussion hosted by the College of Business and Economics. During the panel several professionals
                    discussed their leadership experiences and how communication supports inclusive team environments.
                    I listened to panelists describe how active listening and encouraging team participation leads to
                    stronger decision making. Hearing their workplace examples helped me understand how communication
                    and leadership are closely connected. I appreciated the opportunity to hear different leadership
                    perspectives from experienced professionals. The discussion helped me reflect on how leaders create
                    environments where employees feel comfortable sharing ideas. I developed a stronger understanding
                    of how communication supports collaboration and teamwork. In my future career I hope to apply
                    these lessons by being a thoughtful communicator who values diverse perspectives.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<!-- ── CAREER PREPARATION ── -->
