                    <span class="card-title">Internship – LAZ Parking Web Application Development</span>
                    <span class="card-badge career-badge">5 pts</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">November 2 – December 14, 2025</div>
                <p class="card-reflection">
                    Between November 2 and December 14, 2025 I worked on an internship project developing a web
                    application for LAZ Parking. The goal of the project was to create a tool that could help
                    streamline certain operational processes within the organization. During the project I designed
                    parts of the application structure and thought carefully about how employees would interact with
                    the interface. I evaluated what information the system needed to capture and how it should be
                    organized to support daily operations. I enjoyed working on a real project that could potentially
                    be used in an actual business environment. The experience strengthened my problem-solving skills
                    and helped me become more confident working independently on technical projects. I also learned
                    how technical solutions support larger business processes. In my future career I hope to continue
                    building systems and tools that improve organizational efficiency.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-card-v2">
